Package uk.blankaspect.common.json

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JsonArray
    This class implements a JSON array value.
    JsonBoolean
    This class implements an immutable JSON Boolean value.
    JsonGenerator
    This class implements a generator of JSON text for a JSON value.
    JsonNull
    This class implements a JSON null value.
    JsonNumber
    This class implements an immutable JSON number value.
    JsonObject
    This class implements a JSON object value.
    JsonParser
    This class implements a parser that transforms JSON text into a tree of JSON values.
    JsonString
    This class implements an immutable JSON string value.
    JsonUtils
    This class contains utility methods that relate to JSON.
    JsonValue
    This is the abstract base class of a JSON value.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JsonGenerator.Mode
    This is an enumeration of the modes that control the way in which whitespace is written between the tokens of the JSON text.
    JsonNumber.NumberType
    This is an enumeration of the types of Java number in which the value of a JsonNumber may be stored.
    JsonValue.Kind
    This is an enumeration of the kinds of JSON value.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    JsonArray.ElementKindException
    This class implements an unchecked exception that is thrown by a method that unwraps the elements of a JSON array if it finds that an element is not of the expected kind.
    JsonObject.NoSuchPropertyException
    This class implements an unchecked exception that is thrown when an attempt is made to access a property of a JSON object by name and the JSON object does not contain a property with the specified name.
    JsonParser.ParseException
    This class implements an exception that is thrown if an error occurs when parsing JSON text.
